sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User<br/>(kubectl/oc)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Operator Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant RayCtrl as RayCluster Controller
    participant AppWrapperCtrl as AppWrapper Controller
    participant Kueue as Kueue API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuthServer as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuthProxy as OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RayDashboard as Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant Browser as User Browser

    rect rgb(200, 220, 240)
        Note over User,RayCtrl: Flow 1: Create RayCluster (OpenShift)
        User->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/ray.io/v1/namespaces/{ns}/rayclusters<br/>Auth: User credentials
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-ray-io-v1-raycluster<br/>TLS client cert
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated RayCluster
        K8sAPI->>RayCtrl: Watch event: RayCluster created
        RayCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceAccount<br/>Service Account Token
        RayCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterRoleBinding<br/>Service Account Token
        RayCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create CA Secret<br/>Service Account Token
        RayCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create OAuth Service<br/>Service Account Token
        RayCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Route<br/>Service Account Token
        RayCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>Service Account Token
    end

    rect rgb(220, 240, 220)
        Note over Browser,RayDashboard: Flow 2: Access Ray Dashboard (OpenShift)
        Browser->>OAuthProxy: GET https://{dashboard}-{ns}.{domain}/<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.3
        OAuthProxy->>OAuthServer: Validate session token<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
        OAuthServer-->>OAuthProxy: Token valid
        OAuthProxy->>RayDashboard: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8265 (localhost)
        RayDashboard-->>OAuthProxy: Response
        OAuthProxy-->>Browser: Response (HTTPS)
    end

    rect rgb(240, 220, 200)
        Note over User,AppWrapperCtrl: Flow 3: Create AppWrapper
        User->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/workload.codeflare.dev/v1beta2/appwrappers<br/>Auth: User credentials
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-workload-codeflare-dev-v1beta2-appwrapper<br/>TLS client cert
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated AppWrapper
        K8sAPI->>AppWrapperCtrl: Watch event: AppWrapper created
        AppWrapperCtrl->>Kueue: Create Workload resource<br/>HTTPS/6443 Service Account Token
        Kueue-->>AppWrapperCtrl: Workload admitted
        AppWrapperCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create wrapped resources<br/>(RayCluster, Job, etc.)
    end

    rect rgb(240, 240, 200)
        Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 4: Prometheus Scrapes Metrics
        User->>K8sAPI: ServiceMonitor triggers scrape
        K8sAPI->>RayCtrl: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 (Service Account Token)
        RayCtrl-->>K8sAPI: Prometheus metrics
    end
